#headerwrap
  .container
    .row
      .col-lg-8.col-lg-offset-2
        %h3 Send us a short pitch about your idea
        %h1 Build Your Dream.
    .record-container
      .row.bottom-17
        .col-lg-12
          %video#pitch.video-js.vjs-default-skin{style: 'margin: 0 auto'}
          %h5 (record as many times as you need until you love your pitch)
      .row.bottom-17
        .col-lg-6.col-lg-offset-3
          .input-group.input-fields
            %input#contact-info.form-control.input-lg{:type => 'text', placeholder: 'Enter E-mail or Skype username'}
            %span.input-group-btn
              %input{type: "hidden", name: :fileupload, id: :fileupload}
              %button#send-pitch.btn.btn-success.btn-lg{type: 'submit'} Send us the Pitch!
          .progress
            .progress-bar.progress-bar-success{"aria-valuemax" => "100", "aria-valuemin" => "0", "aria-valuenow" => "60", :role => "progressbar", :style => "width: 60%;"}
              60%
    .done
      .panel.panel-success
        .panel-heading
          %h4.panel-title Upload complete
        .panel-body
          %p
            ðŸŽ‰ You've successfully uploaded your pitch! ðŸŽ‰
          %p
            You'll be hearing from us in the next 24 hours. Remember that you can check any time your feedback status by providing the same E-mail/Skype you used upon submission.
          %p
            %b Thank you for trusting us
    .not-done
      .panel.panel-danger
        .panel-heading
          %h4.panel-title Upload not completed
        .panel-body
          %p
            Oops! Your pitch didn't reach our servers!
          %p
            There was some issue while your pitch was being uploaded, please drop us an e-mail at support@pitchium.com and let us know what exactly happened. If you lost your connectivity, please
            %a{id: 'retry-upload', href: '#'} click here to upload your file again
          %p
            %b Thank you for your patience

